citus-ha (2.0.0) testing; urgency=low

  * Rework of the CLI to `citusha <verb> <object>`

  * CLI can be used to find the uri of the monitor and the formations

  * Added support for a proxy port (eg. the pgbouncer port fronting the database)

  * Added support for a custom listen address that postgres will listen on

  * Keeps the secondary running in read only mode during failover

  * Added a maintenance state to temporarily take a standby out of service without interrupting writes

  * Automatically add worker nodes on the coordinator

  * Worker failover with automatic metadata updates

 -- Nils Dijk <nils@citusdata.com>  Fri, 22 Feb 2019 17:15:00 +0100


